description:
These are subtitles for the Monsters Vs Aliens movie. There seems to be two versions synched for two releases. You need to check to see which one works for you.

There are subs in spanish and english.

They are external subtitles. To use them, rename the file of your choice to exactly the same name as your .avi video file but with a .srt extention.

I.e. if your movie's name is:

&quot;mvs-monsters.avi&quot;

and you want subtitles in english, rename

&quot;Monsters Vs Aliens (english-version-synch2-subtitles).srt&quot;

to

&quot;mvs-monsters.srt&quot;

and use a compatible media player, like vlc from videolan.org or any other compatible with .srt subtitles.
